## Linux Fundamental


1. File System 
### pwd => Print Working Diractory
### cd  => Change Diractory
### ls => Folder Listing
### mkdir => make diractory
### rmdir => remove diractory
### cp => copy file 
### rm => remove file 
### mv => move file .
### locate => search file (kind of window file search)
### passwd => password change 
### man => description for tools
### ls -la => file describ ( permision )
### echo > "file name" text.text => file make
